Titolo: Fighting Masters

Anno: 1991

Descrizione: Fighting Masters is a 1991 fighting video game developed by Almanic Corporation, in conjunction with Aicom and ALU, and published for the Sega Genesis in Japan and later in North America by Treco. In the game, players assume the role of a hero to fight against an assortment of opponents on a apocalyptic setting to face against an entity known as Lord Valgasu. Co-directed by Hajime Kusano and Ram≈ç Kobayashi, the title was created by some of the same team that would later work on various projects at Almanic such as E.V.O.: Search for Eden. It was met with mixed reception from critics since its release.

